      "content": "Hey, just looking over the Q3 R&D roadmap you generated. I'm seeing a massive concentration of resources going into oncology and autoimmune treatments specifically optimized for European genomic profiles. The board is raising concerns that we're ignoring tropical diseases and much larger patient populations in the Global South. We need to see a plan for diversifying our target demographics immediately.",
